definitions.definition: A long peninsula forming part of Kamchatka Krai in the Far East of Russia , lying between the Pacific Ocean and the Sea of Okhotsk .
A krai and federal subject of Russia , in the Russian Far East .
A river in Kamchatka Krai , Russia .
